				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7337949#post-4161769</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7337949/scp-4656#post-4161769</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 22 Feb 2019 16:58:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Emo Squiddy</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3470147</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>An anti-infohazard is a rare kind of information-based anomaly that functions through non-awareness. Whereas a normal infohazard manifests itself by knowledge of or references to its locus endangering subjects, an anti-infohazard manifests itself by lack of knowledge endangering subjects</p> </blockquote> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
